---
// Секция «Unleash the Power of Your» + Download Now / App Store
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-12 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between">
      <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center order-2 md:order-1">
        <div class="relative h-72 w-56 sm:h-80 sm:w-64">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[2.5rem] border-[10px] border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 shadow-xl" style="transform: rotate(-3deg);">
            <div class="absolute inset-2 rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-800" />
            <div class="absolute top-4 left-1/2 h-5 w-20 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-slate-900" />
            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-2">
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-500" />
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-slate-500" />
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-white" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 order-1 md:order-2 md:pl-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Unleash the<br />Power of Your Phone
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">
          Discover how our custom-designed app can revolutionize your phone experience.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-slate-100">
            <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-400 to-pink-500 text-white">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Download Now</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Transform the way you interact with your phone.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-slate-100">
            <span class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-sky-500 text-white">
              <svg class="h-7 w-7" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.81-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Get It on the App Store</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Our innovative app is now available on the App Store.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-20 text-center text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">Partnering for Success</p>
  </div>
</section>
